'Hello again! Ready to help? \n\n'There are many things that need doing out there in Gorgoroth. A huge amount of things! Right now, we really just need you to go out there, and do what needs doing! Check the Bounty Board to see what there is to do.'
There is much to do for the Conquest of Gorgoroth to succeed. This week, you should focus your efforts on Allegiance quests.

'Ah, [placeholder], just who I wanted to see.\n\n'We're overloaded with requests for aid from our allies in Gorgoroth. Right now, the best way for you to help is to get down there and start fixing their problems for them. Check the Bounty Board to see what needs doing.'

'[placeholder], you are just in time.\n\n'Our allies in Gorgoroth are struggling to keep control of the region. They need assistance in the field, and I can think of no one better to send than you. Check the Bounty Board to see who has requested aid.'

'Hail, [placeholder]. Gondor is in need of your services once more.\n\n'We're receiving more and more requests for aid in the regions of Gorgoroth, and I want you to go and do what you can to help in the field. There's no sense in letting the enemy gain a foothold now that we've come this far! Check the Bounty Board for work.'
